FBIS4-68120 "jptot020__l94042" JPRS-TOT-94-020-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 12 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA INDIA `Pakistan-Trained Kashmiri Terrorist' Arrested in Delhi `Pakistan-Trained Kashmiri Terrorist' Arrested in Delhi BK1305011694 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 GMT 12 May 94 BK1305011694 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] Delhi police averted a major tragedy last night by arresting a Pakistan-trained Kashmiri terrorist trying to enter a cinema hall in Connaught Place in New Delhi with a live bomb. The deputy commissioner of police, Mr. Dharmendra Kumar, told newsmen today that the 22-year-old accused, a member of a banned militant outfit, was responsible for the bomb blast in another cinema hall in Connaught Place in January.
